headline: Dine Brands (DIN) Q4 Earnings Miss Estimates
summary: Dine Brands (DIN) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -35.56% and 1.75%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
